</div>
<h3>Expedia</h3>
<p>Expedia is effectively the inverse of Amazon here on my screens, moving from a very organic-friendly desktop layout (with a big organic result, company info, and stories about the company) to a single big branded ad.</p>
<p><strong>Desktop:</strong></p>
<div class="embedded-entity align-center" data-embed-button="images" data-entity-embed-display="view_mode:media.simple_image" data-entity-type="media" data-entity-uuid="e7815bef-9e0d-4973-8c3f-544df337e52e" data-langcode="en">
<article>
