</article>
</div>
<h3>Hewlett Packard</h3>
<p>HP’s desktop result is fairly ad-heavy and features two reseller/competitors, but I can at least see the organic listing and some general company info here. In their mobile result I’m getting virtually all ad, with the tip of some news results: here again it seems likely that many mobile searches will navigate to the site through paid search clicks.</p>
<p><strong>Desktop:</strong></p>
<div class="embedded-entity align-center" data-embed-button="images" data-entity-embed-display="view_mode:media.simple_image" data-entity-type="media" data-entity-uuid="b5ee3183-2832-478d-8b26-2eeeb1615a4a" data-langcode="en">
