</article>
</div>
<h3>Autotrader</h3>
<p>Autotrader’s desktop search allows me to quickly see the organic site (along with multiple site links) and information about the company in addition to the prominently displayed ad. The immediately visible portion of the mobile SERP? All ad.</p>
<p><strong>Desktop:</strong></p>
<div class="embedded-entity align-center" data-embed-button="images" data-entity-embed-display="view_mode:media.simple_image" data-entity-type="media" data-entity-uuid="273843f6-221b-42ac-931f-1933a9df0cf5" data-langcode="en">
