<h3>AT&amp;T</h3>
<p>AT&amp;T’s desktop search once again has a large ad from the brand, but allows me to quickly see the organic listing, a site search box, and sitelinks as well as general company info in the right nav.</p>
<p>Mobile? Just an ad.</p>
<p><strong>Desktop:</strong></p>
<div class="embedded-entity align-center" data-embed-button="images" data-entity-embed-display="view_mode:media.simple_image" data-entity-type="media" data-entity-uuid="367e133f-1d89-4cdc-a9ae-b9ea4a1e64ec" data-langcode="en">
