</div>
<h3>Uline</h3>
<p>Uline continues this trend with a prominent organic listing below the paid listing, organic site links, a site search bar, and company info.</p>
<p>Juxtaposed against the visible part of the mobile SERP: only their ad.</p>
<p><strong>Desktop:</strong></p>
<div class="embedded-entity align-center" data-embed-button="images" data-entity-embed-display="view_mode:media.simple_image" data-entity-type="media" data-entity-uuid="102d510c-1c07-4ec5-894d-83d2b159275a" data-langcode="en">
